OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA few bright spells in the east
OL,6,Fotherwise rather cloudy with scattered
OL,7,Fshowers. These will turn heavy for a
OL,8,Ftime across Caithness and Sutherland
OL,9,Fthis afternoon. Showers becoming light
OL,10,Fand fewer elsewhere this afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FAny showers dying out this
OL,13,Fevening. Then dry with clear spells,
OL,14,Fturning rather chilly in places.
OL,15,FThickening cloud will bring rain to
OL,16,Fthe south later in the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
