OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA cloudy morning with rain
OL,6,Fspreading to all parts. Turning drier
OL,7,Fin the afternoon with a few showers in
OL,8,Fthe west. Some afternoon brightness
OL,9,Fdeveloping around Inverness and Nairn.
OL,10,FWarm.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMainly
OL,13,Fdry and warm on Friday, rain likely by
OL,14,Fevening. Dry, warm and bright over the
OL,15,Fweekend.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
